:\"creative_assistant_agent\",\"actions\":{\"skip_summarization\":null,\"state_delta\":{},\"artifact_delta\":{},\"transfer_to_agent\":\"writing_pipeline\",\"escalate\":null,\"requested_auth_configs\":{},\"requested_tool_confirmations\":{}},\"long_running_tool_ids\":[],\"branch\":null,\"id\":\"e6d32824-44bb-40f7-8d48-ed0d2be1021a\",\"timestamp\":1758939220.118565},{\"content\":{\"parts\":[{\"video_metadata\":null,\"thought\":null,\"inline_data\":null,\"file_data\":null,\"thought_signature\":null,\"function_call\":null,\"code_execution_result\":null,\"executable_code\":null,\"function_response\":null,\"text\":\"**1. K\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch & C\u1ea5u tr\u00fac (D\u00e0n \u00fd):**\\n\\n*   **Gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u:**\\n    *   T\u1ed5ng quan v\u1ec1 \\\"The Crazy Iris and Other Stories of the Atomic Aftermath\\\" v\u00e0 t\u00e1c gi\u1ea3.\\n    *   N\u00eau b\u1eadt ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1 ch\u00ednh: S\u1ef1 gi\u1eb1ng x\u00e9 gi\u1eefa hy v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1ecdng trong cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1ed1ng s\u00f3t sau th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda h\u1ea1t nh\u00e2n.\\n    *   Lu\u1eadn \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u00ednh: Cu\u1ed1n s\u00e1ch kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 s\u00e2u s\u1eafc s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p c\u1ee7a t\u00e2m l\u00fd con ng\u01b0\u1eddi sau th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda, th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ea5u tranh \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm \u00fd ngh\u0129a v\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.\\n\\n*   **Ph\u00e2n t\u00edch c\u00e1c c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n ti\u00eau bi\u1ec3u:**\\n    *   Ch\u1ecdn l\u1ecdc 2-3 truy\u1ec7n ng\u1eafn ti\u00eau bi\u1ec3u th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n r\u00f5 nh\u1ea5t ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1 hy v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1ecdng.\\n    *   *Ph\u00e2n t\u00edch truy\u1ec7n 1:*\\n        *   T\u00f3m t\u1eaft c\u1ed1t truy\u1ec7n.\\n        *   Ph\u00e2n t\u00edch c\u00e1c y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1ecdng (m\u1ea5t m\u00e1t, b\u1ec7nh t\u1eadt, s\u1ef1 h\u1ee7y ho\u1ea1i m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng).\\n  